General.Name: Ageson Bhd
General.Description: Ageson Berhad, an investment holding company, primarily engages in the construction, property development, general trading, and sand mining businesses in Malaysia. It operates through three segments: Construction, Property Development, and Others. The company provides construction services for residential or commercial properties, transportation hubs, infrastructure works, etc. It also develops properties from land acquisition to handover of completed property units to purchasers. In addition, the company is involved in the trading of construction raw materials; export of sand; mineral resource trading activities; lift elevator trading business; piling and construction works; provision of IT related solution services; provision of building and industry technology; and provision of system, software, and hardware solutions. Further, it engages in installation of elevators; provision of mechanical trading services and programmable logic controller activities; and software and system development, as well as acts as a construction contractor. The company was formerly known as Prinsiptek Corporation Berhad and changed its name to Ageson Berhad in November 2019. Ageson Berhad was incorporated in 2002 and is based in Shah Alam, Malaysia.
